the industrial revolution and this should

00:04:40.110 --> 00:04:47.880
have lead to increase in the warming rate.
In climatologist language, four tenth of a

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:52.120
watt per meter. We were putting more
energy into climate but it wasn't turning

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:58.290
up in the global temperature. The question
