in 1997 and 1998. My first year as

00:05:36.010 --> 00:05:41.620
Director of Scripps when my office was
inundated. Then you can see the profile of

00:05:41.620 --> 00:05:47.740
the slowing warming that we've seen
throughout the century. The global mean

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:52.800
temperature that the scientists calculate
is taken from data. Most of it is from

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:58.610
satellite observations of the sea surface
temperature and the sea covers 70 percent

00:05:58.610 --> 00:06:04.850
of the Earth's surface. You would expect
that this computation will be dominated by

00:06:04.850 --> 00:06:11.480
what's happening in the ocean. After many
gyrations the community came to realize

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:17.580
that it was the ocean. It's the behavior
