00:08:34.180 --> 00:08:40.020
Wind, to La Niña sense, larger Trade Wind.
Is continuing to get larger in the

00:08:40.020 --> 00:08:43.630
negative direction that's the negative
part of this curve and it's

00:08:43.630 --> 00:08:48.310
